title: Chori Chori
subTitle: A cavalier young woman claims to be a businessman's fianc√©e and moves into his house. However, seizing the opportunity, the businessman plays along to make his true love jealous.

title: Mahaan
subTitle: A lawyer goes into hiding after being falsely accused of committing a crime, while his wife gives birth to twins. Years later, fate reunites the family under difficult circumstances.

title: Chintu Ji
subTitle: Rishi, the son of a legendary actor, decides to enter politics and go to Hadbahedi, a remote village. However, he creates havoc by misleading the villagers who trust him simply because he is famous.

title: Apmaan Ki Aag
subTitle: While celebrating his girlfriend Mona's birthday, Vikrant gets humiliated by two goons. He vows to exact revenge but it takes him down a difficult and thorny path.

title: Haqeeqat
subTitle: Shiva changes his name to Ajay as he leaves his criminal life after saving a police officer and his family. He falls in love with a widow and marries her, but his past comes back to haunt him.

title: Shershaah
subTitle: Vikram Batra, a young man, dreams of becoming a soldier and falls in love with Dimple. Soon after his training, he climbs the military ranks and contributes to India's victory in the Kargil war.

title: Hum Tumhare Hain Sanam
subTitle: Gopal is happily married to Radha until she meets her friend Suraj and starts obsessing over his singing career. Gopal suspects that they are secretly seeing each other and decides to leave her.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Benaam
subTitle: Amit and Sheela, a married couple, save a stabbing victim from an attempted murder. However, things take a dark turn when they start receiving death threats from an unknown person.

title: Aladin
subTitle: Aladin, an orphan tormented by bullies, discovers a magic lamp that grants him incredible powers. Later, with the help of a genie, he embarks on thrilling adventures to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Deedar
subTitle: The marriage plans of Anand and Sapna are thwarted when it is revealed that Anand's business tycoon father had previously framed Sapna's father for a crime he did not commit.

title: Happy New Year
subTitle: Shuffling between old grudges and new grooves, Charlie and his friends bumble their way through an international dance competition to break into a heavily guarded vault of diamonds.

title: Main Hoon Na
subTitle: Major Ram is given orders to go undercover as a college student to protect a general's daughter from a rogue soldier. He must also fulfil his dying father's desire to reconcile with his family.

title: Gharwali Baharwali
subTitle: Arun inadvertently ties the knot with Manisha and even has a child with her. He keeps this a secret from his first wife Kaajal. It is only a matter of time before his life starts to unravel.

title: Arjun Pandit
subTitle: A mild-mannered professor's world shatters after betrayal drives him into a violent transformation, where love and rage collide on the streets of Mumbai.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: Takkar
subTitle: Ravi Malhotra, a photographer, is framed by a corrupt policeman, D'Costa, on the day before his wedding. While in jail, Ravi studies law to exact revenge against his perpetrator.

title: Action Replayy
subTitle: A son tries to revive his parents' lifeless marriage by travelling back in time to the 70s when their romance was budding. To his surprise, this turns out to be more complex than he first expected.

title: Garv: Pride and Honour
subTitle: An honest officer falls prey to a corrupt system where he is dismissed from the police force for getting involved in a murder case while trying to arrest a few corrupt politicians.

title: Baghban
subTitle: Raj and Pooja live an upsetting life when their sons refuse to reciprocate their affections and take care of them.

title: Talaash: The Hunt Begins
subTitle: Arjun grows up to be a high-profile vigilante after his father's murder and sister's abduction. Soon, he vows revenge and sets out on a mission to find his sister.

title: Raja Hindustani
subTitle: Raja, a taxi driver, falls in love with Aarti, a rich girl and marries her against her parents' wishes. Later, her stepmother tries to create differences between the couple.

title: Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam
subTitle: A newly-wed man discovers that his wife is in love with another man and decides to unite them. Ignoring the ridicule he might have to face for this, he takes his wife to Italy in search of her love.
